Just stand up and tell what you have got it for.

762
01:02:46,200 --> 01:02:48,720
SY: This is rose water.
SM: Loudly.

763
01:02:48,920 --> 01:02:51,720
Rose water, made from rose petals. They fell in Scotland

764
01:02:51,920 --> 01:02:54,960
on Guru day, today, three days ago, on Thursday.

765
01:02:55,160 --> 01:02:57,800
And from Highland spring water.

766
01:02:58,000 --> 01:03:01,240
so that we bow with washing Mother's Feet with this rose water

767
01:03:01,440 --> 01:03:06,520
offering the Guru tatwa of Scotland and all nations.

768
01:03:06,760 --> 01:03:08,480
with Mother's blessings.

769
01:03:08,680 --> 01:03:12,440
Put it in that water so that....

770
01:03:15,800 --> 01:03:18,080
Let our ears hear that which is true,

771
01:03:18,280 --> 01:03:20,400
let our eyes see that which is pure,

772
01:03:20,600 --> 01:03:23,400
let our beings praise that which is divine,

773
01:03:23,640 --> 01:03:28,560
and let those who listen hear not my voice but the wisdom of God.

774
01:03:29,080 --> 01:03:32,120
Let us worship with the same song, the same strength

775
01:03:32,320 --> 01:03:36,880
and the same knowledge and let our meditation enlighten and enrich.

776
01:03:37,200 --> 01:03:40,520
Let there be amongst us compassion and peace.

777
01:03:40,720 --> 01:03:42,680
Now the prayer:

778
01:03:42,960 --> 01:03:46,280
Salutation to Shr Ganesh, sksht Shr Jesus

779
01:03:46,480 --> 01:03:49,480
Sksht Shr Nirmal Devyai namo namah.

780
01:03:49,680 --> 01:03:52,280
It is You who is the beginning of all the beginnings.

781
01:03:52,480 --> 01:03:55,600
It is You who is the doer of all deeds which have been done,

782
01:03:55,800 --> 01:03:57,720
are being done, and will be done.

783
01:03:57,920 --> 01:04:00,840
It is You who supports all things that are supported.

784
01:04:01,040 --> 01:04:04,040
It is You who protects all things that are protected.

785
01:04:04,240 --> 01:04:06,960
It is You who is the complete, all-pervading Spirit,

786
01:04:07,160 --> 01:04:09,160
Gods divine energy.

787
01:04:09,360 --> 01:04:12,200
Think clearly brain, speak only the truth.

788
01:04:12,440 --> 01:04:15,680
Let Your presence, awakened in us by Kundalini, speak;

789
01:04:15,880 --> 01:04:19,160
let Your presence, awakened in us by Kundalini, listen;

790
01:04:19,360 --> 01:04:22,920
let Your presence, awakened in us by Kundalini, bless;

791
01:04:23,160 --> 01:04:26,720
let Your presence, awakened in us by Kundalini, protect;

792
01:04:26,920 --> 01:04:29,760
let Your presence, awakened by Kundalini in us,

793
01:04:29,960 --> 01:04:32,640
Your disciples, be the disciple.

794
01:04:32,960 --> 01:04:36,320
You are the essence of all the sacred literature and holy words

795
01:04:36,520 --> 01:04:39,440
and You are the energy that understands the holy words.

796
01:04:39,640 --> 01:04:42,440
You are the divine combination of complete truth,

797
01:04:42,640 --> 01:04:46,200
complete happiness and complete energy; and You are beyond.

798
01:04:46,400 --> 01:04:50,000
You are all knowledge, and You are the use to which knowledge is put

799
01:04:50,200 --> 01:04:52,680
You exist until the end of all things,

800
01:04:52,880 --> 01:04:55,160
and after the end of all things You are.

801
01:04:55,360 --> 01:04:58,240
You create the end of all things, and after the end of all things,

802
01:04:58,440 --> 01:05:00,000
You remain indifferent.

803
01:05:00,200 --> 01:05:03,520
You are the earth, You are the water, You are the fire,

804
01:05:03,720 --> 01:05:06,640
You are the air, and You are the space above the air.

805
01:05:06,840 --> 01:05:09,320
You are the gunas and You are beyond the gunas.

806
01:05:09,520 --> 01:05:11,680
You are the body and You are beyond the body.

807
01:05:11,880 --> 01:05:15,040
You are the essence of time and You are beyond time.

808
01:05:15,240 --> 01:05:18,000
You and only You exist at the Muladhara chakra.

809
01:05:18,200 --> 01:05:20,880
You are the Spirit and You are beyond the Spirit;

810
01:05:21,080 --> 01:05:23,920
and those who would join God meditate upon You

811
01:05:24,120 --> 01:05:28,560
You are Brahma, Vishnu, Rudra; You are Indra, Agni, Vayu;

812
01:05:28,840 --> 01:05:31,640
You are the sun at noon, You are the full moon;

813
01:05:31,880 --> 01:05:33,160
through all of these and more,

814
01:05:33,360 --> 01:05:36,840
You are the all-pervading energy of innocence and wisdom.

815
01:05:37,160 --> 01:05:41,280
You are the divine servant who stoops to wash the feet of saints;

816
01:05:41,480 --> 01:05:43,400
You are the tiny core of all things,

817
01:05:43,600 --> 01:05:46,000
without which the large have no purpose;

818
01:05:46,200 --> 01:05:49,360
You are the key to the libraries of all the scriptures,

819
01:05:49,560 --> 01:05:51,480
without which the truth is hidden;

820
01:05:51,720 --> 01:05:54,320
You are the full stop which completes the sentence,

821
01:05:54,520 --> 01:05:56,960
and without which the sentence loses its meaning.

822
01:05:57,160 --> 01:05:58,720
You are the crescent moon,

823
01:05:58,920 --> 01:06:01,560
You are the stars and You are beyond the stars;

824
01:06:01,800 --> 01:06:04,880
all the things, from tiny dot to universe, is You.

825
01:06:05,080 --> 01:06:06,840
You are not to put your hand inside.

826
01:06:07,040 --> 01:06:09,800
Just pour water on My Feet when he says the mantras.

827
01:06:10,000 --> 01:06:11,720
You are where the sounds combine;

828
01:06:11,920 --> 01:06:14,680
You are the silence between the sounds;

829
01:06:14,920 --> 01:06:17,800
You are the rhythm of all music and all prayers.

830
01:06:18,040 --> 01:06:20,360
This is the knowledge of Nirmal Ganesh,

831
01:06:20,560 --> 01:06:23,520
and You, Nirmal Ganesh, are the master of that knowledge,

832
01:06:23,720 --> 01:06:27,440
and all knowledge. You are the God and You are the Goddess.

833
01:06:27,640 --> 01:06:30,160
Aum Gam Nirmal Ganapataye

834
01:06:30,360 --> 01:06:33,080
To Your powers, Ganesha, let all surrender;

835
01:06:33,280 --> 01:06:35,840
and the left side of memory and the right side of action

836
01:06:36,040 --> 01:06:39,640
surrender to You. And let Your enlightenment prevail.

837
01:06:39,840 --> 01:06:43,160
Your first tooth You have, and four hands:

838
01:06:43,360 --> 01:06:45,640
one holding a rope, the second a goad,

839
01:06:45,840 --> 01:06:49,360
the third is raised in blessing and the fourth offers sustenance.

840
01:06:49,560 --> 01:06:52,960
Your banner is that of a humble mouse.

841
01:06:53,160 --> 01:06:55,640
You have long ears and are clothed in red.

842
01:06:55,840 --> 01:06:59,200
Red decorates You and You are worshipped with red flowers.

843
01:06:59,400 --> 01:07:01,640
You have compassion for those who love You,

844
01:07:01,840 --> 01:07:05,080
and it is for those who love You that You come to this Earth.

845
01:07:05,280 --> 01:07:08,000
You are the force that creates, the energy that pervades

846
01:07:08,200 --> 01:07:09,880
and the Spirit that protects.

847
01:07:10,080 --> 01:07:12,960
Those who seek union with God pray to You.

848
01:07:13,160 --> 01:07:15,880
Those who seek union with God worship You.

849
01:07:16,080 --> 01:07:19,120
Aum Gam Nirmal Jesusye.

850
01:07:19,360 --> 01:07:22,360
To Your powers, Aum Jesus, let's all surrender;

851
01:07:22,560 --> 01:07:25,160
let the left side of memory and the right side of action

852
01:07:25,360 --> 01:07:29,000
surrender to You and let Your enlightenment prevail.

853
01:07:29,440 --> 01:07:31,240
You are the Word that was the beginning;

854
01:07:31,440 --> 01:07:33,760
You are the Word that will be the ending.

855
01:07:33,960 --> 01:07:37,400
You are He who was born of a virgin, and died on the cross.

856
01:07:37,600 --> 01:07:41,440
You are He who absorbs all sins, and who died to live again.

857
01:07:41,640 --> 01:07:46,280
You are God in man, and You are worshipped with red flowers.

858
01:07:46,840 --> 01:07:49,240
You have compassion for those who love You,

859
01:07:49,440 --> 01:07:52,880
and it is for those who love You that You come to this Earth.

860
01:07:53,080 --> 01:07:56,560
You are the force that creates, the energy that pervades

861
01:07:56,760 --> 01:07:58,680
and the Spirit that protects.

862
01:07:58,880 --> 01:08:02,040
Those who seek union with God pray through You.

863
01:08:02,240 --> 01:08:05,600
Those who seek union with God worship You.

864
01:08:05,800 --> 01:08:10,800
Shri Ganesha, salutations to You. Shri Jesus, salutations to You.

865
01:08:11,080 --> 01:08:14,840
He who is the beginning of all worship, salutations to You.

866
01:08:15,040 --> 01:08:19,840
He who destroys all the powers of evil, salutations to You.

867
01:08:20,040 --> 01:08:22,080
Sksht son of Lord Shiva,

868
01:08:22,280 --> 01:08:25,400
who is unending blessings, salutations to You.

869
01:08:25,600 --> 01:08:28,240
Sksht son of Mary Mtj,

870
01:08:28,440 --> 01:08:31,560
who is unending love, salutations to You.

871
01:08:31,760 --> 01:08:34,600
Sksht Mtj Nirmal Dev,

872
01:08:34,800 --> 01:08:38,680
who is unending joy, salutations to You.

873
01:08:40,800 --> 01:08:44,000
Now the Sanskrit verses

874
01:08:44,200 --> 01:08:46,920
which are being translated in English as you heard it

875
01:08:47,120 --> 01:08:50,560
will be said, at the time when they'll be pouring water on My Feet,

876
01:08:50,760 --> 01:08:53,800
called as abhisheka.

877
01:08:55,600 --> 01:08:57,480
Loud speak.

878
01:09:06,840 --> 01:09:09,840
Slowly.

879
01:09:11,760 --> 01:09:14,280
You have to put hand, to hold it up.

880
01:13:24,080 --> 01:13:26,520
See now viniyoga, the word has come -

881
01:13:26,640 --> 01:13:28,160
the spending of it.

882
01:13:28,480 --> 01:13:33,040
What is the spending of the name of Shri Ganesha?

883
01:13:33,360 --> 01:13:37,280
When you remember Him, then where do you spend it?

884
01:13:37,520 --> 01:13:41,360
Viniyog, is a very good word.

885
01:14:11,720 --> 01:14:14,520
All right. The girls come.

886
01:14:18,880 --> 01:14:22,120
No, unmarried.

887
01:15:02,240 --> 01:15:07,999
Now they will read about Shri Mahavishnu in English,

888
01:15:08,999 --> 01:15:12,280
who was an incarnation,

889
01:15:13,160 --> 01:15:15,920
came on this Earth as Lord Jesus Christ.

890
01:15:16,200 --> 01:15:18,120
How He was created

891
01:15:18,320 --> 01:15:23,960
and the essence of it was that of ....

892
01:15:27,280 --> 01:15:30,520
That when, was the One,

893
01:15:30,800 --> 01:15:33,440
had the essence of Shri Ganesha

894
01:15:33,720 --> 01:15:39,080
and He came on this earth ultimately as Shri Lord Shri Jesus Christ.

895
01:15:39,320 --> 01:15:41,880
But how He became Mahavishnu

896
01:15:42,120 --> 01:15:44,999
and what were His blessings we should say,

897
01:15:45,200 --> 01:15:48,680
who was the Son of Shri Krishna.

